# Governance Boundaries

## Required contracts
- Input schema: `tools/review/schemas/change_proposal.schema.json`
- Output schema: `tools/review/schemas/governance_decision.schema.json`

## Required analyzers
- template compliance
- architecture boundary
- protected paths
- spec coverage
- YAML validation

## Rules
- Deterministic checks block or escalate first.
- Semantic review is conditional and advisory/escalatory only.
- Aggregation must preserve all findings.
- Waivers must be explicit, time-bounded, and policy-driven.
